---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Program Requirements" description="RACP Basic Training learning, teaching, and assessment program requirements.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Program Requirements</h1>
    <p>Learning, teaching, and assessment — what's required and when.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Learning Program</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Clinical Experience</div>
      <p>36 months full-time equivalent (FTE) in a mix of approved training rotations — in any sequence over the course of training.</p>
    </div>
    <h3>Rotation Plans</h3>
    <p>1 rotation plan per training rotation, submitted at the start of each rotation.</p>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Due 28 February — for rotations in the first half of the year</li>
      <li>Due 31 August — for rotations in the second half of the year</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Teaching Program</h2>
    <p>
      The teaching program guides supervisors, assessors, and accredited training settings to plan
      and deliver teaching activities.
    </p>
    <h3>Required Supervision Roles</h3>
    <p>Each trainee must have named individuals or entities for the following roles (people may hold multiple roles):</p>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Network Director <span class="tag">where a network exists</span></li>
      <li>Director of Physician Education</li>
      <li>Progress Review Panel</li>
      <li>Education Supervisor</li>
      <li>Rotation Supervisor</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Assessment Program</h2>
    <p>Minimum requirements per phase of training (each year):</p>

    <div class="stat-grid">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-number">12</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Learning captures — min. 1 per month</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-number">12</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Observation captures — min. 1 per month</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3>Rotation Progress Reports</h3>
    <p>1 report per training rotation (minimum one per three months), completed at the end of each rotation.</p>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Example</div>
      <p>5 training rotations in Foundation phase → 5 rotation progress reports</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">2 × 6-month rotations in Foundation phase → 4 rotation progress reports (1 per 3 months)</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Phase Progress Reports</h3>
    <p>2 per phase — 1 mid-phase report and 1 end-of-phase report.</p>

    <h3>Examinations</h3>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Written Examination</div>
      <p>1 — early in the Completion phase</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Clinical Examination</div>
      <p>1 — mid-way through the Completion phase</p>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted);">
      These are minimum requirements. More work-based assessments are encouraged.
      Directors of Physician Education and Education Supervisors may require additional assessments.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
